query:
INSERT INTO GithubLinks (
                github_link_id,
                user_id,
                external_github_id,
                external_github_login,
                access_token,
                refresh_token,
                access_token_expires_at,
                refresh_token_expires_at
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8)
            RETURNING github_link_id
